User experience (UX) and user interface (UI) design. Reactive web design. Introduction into Bootstrap and Vue.js frameworks. Programming language JavaScript. AI in web development. The final project will be completed as a practical group work.Objectives/eesmärkid:  This course provides an overview of modern web development technologies. The main goal of the course is to give students the necessary basic knowledge to design and create simple webpages; obtain web development skills while working on own project. No prior web development experience is required, but basic programming skills are a plus.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  On successful completion of this course, a student is able to: * follow the basic principles of web design when creating web pages; * use the web development technologies learned when creating simple web pages.
